  <name>Simbuto</name>
  <summary>a simple graphical budgeting tool</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
    Simbuto is a simple graphical budgeting tool to plan your finances.
    You tell Simbuto at which points in time you have what costs and income 
    and it creates a graph showing you your total assets over time in the future.
    </p>
  </description>

